/* III Stage-0 Ring 0 codegen — cg_r0.c port to .iii.
 * Windows kernel-mode (.sys / Driver/Cycle dispatch).  ABI-compatible with
 * cg_r0.h.  Singleton state, MS x64 calling convention, SEH frame brackets,
 * 28-entry IRP dispatch table, IRQL/SAL/D14 secmem emission.  All AST and
 * file I/O routed through accessor surfaces (NIH, no third-party libs).
 */

